<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٧ - عبد الله بن الْفضل<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَاحِد:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>عَن نَافِع بن جُبَير،<span class="c5"> عَن ابْن عَبَّاس:</span> الأيم أَحَق بِنَفسِهَا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٤٨ - عبد الله بن عبد الله بن جَابر بن عتِيك<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">اثْنَان:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>١ -<span class="c5"> جَاءَنَا ابْن عمر فَقَالَ:</span> هَل تَدْرِي مَا الثَّلَاث الَّتِي دَعَا بِهن رَسُول الله <span class="c4">[<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>] حِين صلى فِي مَسْجِدكُمْ؟<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>